title: Towards Visually Interpreting Variational Autoencoders
details: R Li, W Liu, M Zheng, M Torop, M Rajadhyaksha, J Dy… - 2024
abstract: Recent advances in convolutional neural network (CNN) interpretability have led to a wide-variety of gradient-based visual attention techniques for generating visual attention maps. However, most of these methods require a classification-type design …
